{"tid":1273153,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"需要極多人手做鍵盤戰士帶Facebook 直播風向（一定要置頂）","createTime":"2019-07-01T13:39:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-01T14:03:02.000Z","uid":254923,"like":26,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"9fe2967a89bf0abf638f26b07311c07509e9103a","tid":1273153,"uid":254923,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T13:39:59.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">成王敗寇</span></span><br />\n今日成功爭取嘅話，道理自然就會喺我哋呢邊<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">失敗左嘅話，我哋自然就係暴民</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n依家係好多直播頻道有<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">好多人仲用緊和理非角度</span></span>，又話太暴力。又話過分。<br />\n但而家成件事已經冇得返轉頭，唔可以再分化<br />\n依家要做嘅第一件事<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">改變風氣</span></span><br />\n可以試吓係Facebook 直播 orIG留言：<br />\n<br />\n1.依家二百萬人和平示威都冇用，依家咁樣做係幫香港人增加緊談判籌碼！<br />\n<br />\n2.面對三條人命，林鄭月娥今朝依然舉杯慶祝，唔好再同我講啲咩暴力唔暴力！<br />\n<br />\n3.呢一個月和平理性爭取左啲咩？請尊重現場人士決定！而家互相譴責嘅話，最終被清算嘅係全部人<br />\n<br />\n4.不分化，不割席，各自做各自，團結要一致！如果唔係所有人都會係輸家<br />\n<br />\n全部人同我立即push上熱門<br />\n呢個真係好緊要，要盡可能得到大家嘅認同支持先，！<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"27b5a87b8edfba1d0022ff5cfaf88cbdc365a5ec","tid":1273153,"uid":254923,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T13:40:20.000Z","msg":"依家第一件事係要穩定民心<br />\n一定要推啊冇時間開心住"},{"pid":"bdc4ed63d790425d9b32bb89e7adb4bb11a2d4a9","tid":1273153,"uid":244553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T13:40:22.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"bb565f4ccc97213e9dcfb206e0a53979ba9fb429","tid":1273153,"